WEBVTT

00:08:30.127 --> 00:08:32.306
Unutrašnji bol uvek izviri.

00:08:33.068 --> 00:08:34.218
Uvek.

00:08:34.863 --> 00:08:36.395
A ko plaća ceh?

00:08:37.244 --> 00:08:38.649
Mi.

00:08:38.673 --> 00:08:39.823
Naša deca,

00:08:40.696 --> 00:08:41.846
naše kolege,

00:08:43.354 --> 00:08:44.504
naše zajednice.

00:08:49.354 --> 00:08:50.936
Sad, da me pogrešno ne shvatite.

00:08:51.203 --> 00:08:52.841
Nisam protiv sreće.

00:08:54.213 --> 00:08:55.522
Volim kad sam srećna.

00:08:55.546 --> 00:08:57.133
Prilično sam srećna osoba.

00:08:58.181 --> 00:09:03.958
Međutim, kada potisnemo normalna osećanja
kako bismo prigrlili lažnu pozitivnost,